 Gui5-hiam2 e5 liong5-sim. “Jiat8-sim” (heng5 22:3) 
 A-lek8-san-tai7 bat kong2, "Tng liong5-sim tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 kng chio3 e5 si5, thang kong2 si7 chit8 e5 chin ko-siong7 e5 koan5-se3, chong2-si7 tng lan2 teh gu5-gong7, hoan7-choe7 a2-si7 choe3 ke3-thau5 e5 su7 e5 si5, chit khoan2 e5 koan5-lat8 beh hou7 lan2 tui3-tek8 Ki-tok." Bat u7 In3-tou7 lang5, tui3 Eng-kok e5 chip-cheng3-koaN kong2, "Goan2 e5 liong5-sim kah goan2 na7 tiong7-hu si2, hu7-jin5-lang5 tioh8 sio ti7 sio sin-si e5 chha5-tui-nih8." Eng-kok koaN in3 kong2, "Lin2 na7 an2-ni choe3, goan2 e5 liong5-sim kah goan2 tioh8 chiong lin2 tiau3-si2." 
 Sin oah8-mia7. "Chu2, goa2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?" (Heng7 22: 10) 
 Lou7-tek si7 bou2 sou2-chai7 e5 toa7 kho-hak8-ka, chit8-pai2 i theh8 chit8-chang5 chhiu7, chit chang5 chhiu7 chin hoan2-siong5, au7-lai5 piN3-kau3 chin phaiN2-khoaN3, koh u7 tok8. Chong2-si7 keng-ke3 chit-ui7 kho-hak8-ka, eng7 hoat-tou7 ka7 i oaN7-sin, i long2-chong2 e5 ku7-sip8-koan3 tui3 an2-ni bo5-khi3, i e5 leng5-lek8 liam5-piN u7 sin e5 hoat-tian2, koh chiaN5-choe3 chit8-chang5 kho2-ai3 oe7 kiat-sit8 e5 chhiu7. Lang5 oe7 eng7 hoat-sut8 khi3 choe3 hit-khoan2 e5 ki5-su7, chiong chhiu7 e5 ku7-sip8-koan3 tu5-khi3 hou7 i piN3-choe3 sui2 koh oe7 kiat-sit8. Ho5-hong3 Siong7-te3 kiam2 boe7 choe3 chhut ki5 e5 su7, hou7 chit8 e5 lang5 li7-khui ku7 e5 sip8-koan3, koh teng5 chhong3-cho7 i choe3 chit8 e5 cheng3-tit8 chiaN5-seng3 e5 lang5 mah? 
 Li2 si7 po-le5-tu5 a2-m7-si7? "Siong7-te3 hun-piat goa2, hoaN-hi2 eng7 I e5 KiaN2 chi2-si7 goa2." (Ka-liap8-thai3 1: 15, 16) 
