 I sou2 sit-loh8 e5. "Goa2 khoaN3 ban7-su7 choe3 u7 sun2-hai7, in-ui7 goa2 liah8 jin7-bat Ia5-sou choe3 te7-it ho2 e5." (Hui 3: 8) 
 U7 chit8 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 bo5 kau3 chin ho2-giah8. I kau3 chin oaN3 chiah lai5 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5. Chit8 jit8 i kap i e5 cha-bou2-sun ti7 siaN5-nih8 e5 koe-lou7 teh kiaN5, chit8 e5 khit-chiah8 lai5 chiong ka-ki7 e5 su7 kong2 hou7 in thiaN. Lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 thiaN-liau2 lin5-bin2 i, tui3 te7-a2 theh8-chhut poaN3 khou-gun5 hou7 i. 
 Koh kiaN5 bo5 joa7-hng7, koh u7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 teh theng3-hau7 in lin5-bin2 i, i ia7 hiat chit8 khou-gun5 ti7 i e5 te7-a2. I e5 sun khoaN3 i an2-ni choe3 chiu7 kong2, "An2-ma2 li2 tui3 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 i2-au7, u7 sit-loh8 chin-choe7, u7 iaN2 bo5?" I in3 kong2, "U7-iaN2, goa2 u7 sit-loh8 goa2 e5 kip-seng3, phoe-pheng5 pat8 lang5, phah-sng2 si5 khi3 kiu5 bo5 i3-su3 e5 khoai3-lok8, goa2 ia7 u7 sit-loh8 tham-sim kap kou3-ki2 sim, goa2 sit8-chai7 sit-loh8 chin-choe7." 
 Thang kiaN e5 mng7. "Chio2 cheng3 chio2 siu." (II Lim5 9: 6) 
