 Ho2 ni5-tang. "Ia7 choe7 e5, siu-seng5 ia7 choe7." (II Lim5 9: 6) 
 Choe7-choe7 ni5-cheng5, u7 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 Bi2-kok-lang5, lu2-heng5 ti7 Bi2-kok e5 bou2 seng2. Chit8-pai2 jit8 i2-keng loh8-soaN, i kau3 chit8 e5 choh-chhan5 lang5 e5 chhu3, chhiaN2 in hit-e5-hng hou7 i hioh ti7-hia, in chin hoaN-hi2 chiap-lap8 i. 
